    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that Monte Carlo UQ demonstrates NIH remains below the clinical threshold with margin at all five operating points, and that the geometry smoothing revision introduced in November 2025 is characterised in the revision log as non-material to haemolysis prediction. The team noted that the primary experimental dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-14) predates the modelRevisionDate (2025-11-03) but concluded that the 20-day interval and the limited scope of the geometric change did not warrant a full re-validation campaign prior to submission. This determination was made without formal re-validation evidence and constitutes an unresolved epistemic gap under W-EP-03.",
